<h3 id="next-steps">Next steps</h3>

<p>Now that the lesson has been translated, we are excited to see how it works in practice. Please let us know if you have the chance to teach this lesson to Spanish-speaking learners either as a stand-alone lesson or as part of a two-day workshop. Hereâ€™s a link to all the lessons in Spanish. If you are looking for resources for hosting workshops, please visit the <a href="https://docs.carpentries.org/topic_folders/hosts_instructors/index.html">Carpentries Handbook</a>.</p>

